How to run Super Mario Bros with JPC

In the shell:
1- make application
2- java -Xmx512m -XX:MaxPermSize=128m -jar JPCApplication.jar -fda resources/images/floppy.img hd-a resources/images/dosgames.img -boot fda

In JPC:
3- Select Disks -> HDO[none] -> Choose image -> resources -> images -> dosgames.img -> Load HDO Image

Inside DOS:
4- c -> Type Key (select ":" before hitting Type Key)
5- cd MARIO
6- mario
7- hit space bar
8- check keys -> hit space bar to start
9- pick number of lives (hit a number in your keyboard)
10- play

